            <div class="field field--name-field-slide-header field--type-string field--label-hidden field--count-1 field__item">Technology Solutions in Healthcare</div>
      
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-slide-caption field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--count-1 field__item"><p>Despite market uncertainty, construction activity is maintaining momentum. Multiple mega projects are launching as ongoing maintenance and renovation work forges ahead. Throughout the Midwest, concern about available skilled manpower is growing amid an already tight labor market.</p>
