            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-long-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--count-1 field__item"><p class="large">Buildings have a profound effect on how we live, work and play — and Pepper's values demand that we turn this big idea into action.&nbsp;</p>

